description: Creates an Amazon Chime account under the administrator's AWS account. Only Team account types are currently supported for this action. For more information about different account types, see Managing Your Amazon Chime Accounts in the Amazon Chime Administration Guide.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name of the Amazon Chime account.

nested_items.name: AccountType
nested_items.description: The Amazon Chime account type. For more information about different account types, see Managing Your Amazon Chime Accounts in the Amazon Chime Administration Guide.

nested_items.name: CreatedTimestamp
nested_items.description: The Amazon Chime account creation timestamp, in ISO 8601 format.

nested_items.name: DefaultLicense
nested_items.description: The default license for the Amazon Chime account.

nested_items.name: SupportedLicenses
nested_items.description: Supported licenses for the Amazon Chime account.

nested_items.name: SigninDelegateGroups
nested_items.description: The sign-in delegate groups associated with the account.
